Summary of modifications in this fork:

- Removed the Tauri 2.0 desktop shell (src-tauri/, Cargo, Rust commands,
  bundling targets, auto-updater).
- Reimplemented all Rust-backed functionality in the browser:
    * JSON parse/format/minify/validate/stats/escape (JSON + JSON5 +
      Infinity/NaN sanitization fallback).
    * YAML / XML / TOML / CSV conversion via js-yaml, fast-xml-parser,
      @iarna/toml, and papaparse (lazy-loaded).
    * Code generation via quicktype-core; protobuf / thrift dropped.
    * Image export via html-to-image + browser download.
- Removed desktop-only features: file system access, folder watching,
  native menus, global shortcuts, always-on-top, auto-update.
- Added Cloudflare Pages-ready static build (SvelteKit adapter-static +
  static/_redirects).
